Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子也是这里的毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好年轻喔
