Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:10.95,SongJap,,0,0,0,,ほら まぶしく光る湖は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:25.39,SongChn,,0,0,0,,成为镜子映出那天失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:18.15,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K120}ano {\K60}hi {\K70}ni {\K60}{\K50}na{\K40}ku{\K40}shi{\K60}ta {\K60}mo{\K50}no {\K60}wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:18.15,SongJap,,0,0,0,,あの日に失くしたものを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:25.39,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}utsu{\K60}shi{\K60}da{\K60}su {\K50}{\K40}ka{\K40}ga{\K60}mi {\K200}ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:25.39,SongJap,,0,0,0,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:35.37,SongChn,,0,0,0,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:35.37,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:35.37,SongJap,,0,0,0,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:43.41,SongChn,,0,0,0,,闭上心灵的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:53.52,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}ko{\K60}ko{\K60}ro {\K100}no {\K70}hi{\K50}to{\K50}mi {\K60}to{\K40}ji{\K70}te  {\K60}{\K70}so{\K70}tto {\K80}{\K70}so{\K70}ra {\K110}wo {\K110}da{\K220}ku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:53.52,SongJap,,0,0,0,,心の瞳閉じて そっと空を抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:53.52,SongChn,,0,0,0,,轻轻地拥抱天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回也一定要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原本毫无关系的两人\N在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这不光只有开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以前彼此看不见的部份\N现在都渐渐看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,正面的部份，负面的部份
